# ASCII Art Test
# Tests multi-line ASCII art rendering with echo -e
Output examples/svgs/figlet.svg

Set Theme dark
Set Template macos
Set Title "FIGLET Art Demo"
Set LineHeight 1

Type "figlet -f larry3d dvd | lolcat -f -p 1"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Type "figlet -f isometric3 dvd | lolcat -f"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
